   <body>
      <prereq>
         <note>If shutdown via the display has been disabled, all commands
to shut down or reboot the UPS system have been disabled. The only
way to turn off the UPS is by using the system enable switch on the
front of the UPS by removing all sources.</note>
      </prereq>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Press down the ON and OFF buttons simultaneously to shut
down the UPS.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Wait 20 seconds for the display to power down.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Press the ON button to reboot the UPS.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <note>To perform the UPS shutdown, the load must be disconnected
form the UPS or the load must be supplied by the external bypass.</note>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
      </ol>
